items.title: Alpha Mate Who Cried Wolf (63 episodes)
items.description: When a wolf brutally kills Astrid’s mother, her peaceful life falls apart. Her loving father becomes abusive, blaming her for her mother’s death and the miserable life they now have. She carries this guilt everywhere until she meets Ryker, who seems to understand her more than she does herself. He claims to be her mate, and Astrid feels a strange connection.

items.title: Shy Beauty and The Billionaire Beast (71 episodes)
items.description: When Ana accidentally spills coffee on cold-hearted billionaire Jaxon, ruining his luxury shirt, he demands she pays for it. Refusing to compensate for a 'stupid shirt,' Ana is given an ultimatum: pay in cash or spend one night with him in bed. When Ana declines his indecent proposal, he offers her a job as his secretary. Will she take it?
